      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in showroom condition, featuring flawless exterior surfaces and a pristine interior environment. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering an experience indistinguishable from new. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who demands absolute excellence.",
