    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total gem\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it's basically in perfect shape. If you're looking for something that's been truly babied, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! Let's get you behind the wheel of this beauty.",
