    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. This example features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural vulnerability\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from factory-spec bushings and a variable M-differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetics match the mechanical excellence, featuring a pristine undercarriage and zero paint imperfections. For the purist seeking telepathic hydraulic steering feedback and an 8,000 RPM redline, this is the definitive specimen.",
